@startuml viewtrips
title View Trips Operation Sequence  

actor Client
participant "RailSearchApp (UI)" as UI
participant "BookingSystem" as BS
participant "BookingStorage" as DB

Client -> UI: Enter lastName, govId
UI -> BS: viewTrips(lastName, govId)

activate BS
BS -> DB: findByLastNameAndId(lastName, govId)
DB --> BS: trips[]

BS -> BS: partitionTrips(trips)\n-- current/future vs history --

alt any trips found
  BS --> UI: success({current: [...], history: [...]})
else none found
  BS --> UI: error(\"no trips for provided credentials\")
end
deactivate BS

UI --> Client: Show trips (tabs: Current/Future, History)
@enduml
